Users: purpose clear
Groups:
    groups of users.
    All ACL is done on *groups*
    Each user gets a group with only them in it when they register
        no group is an administrator of this group.
    ACL on groups is all a simple "read, write, admin" ala moinmoin
Problems:
    ACL:
        - list of groups that can change or delete this
        - list of groups that can specify this inclusion of this in a set
ProblemSets:
    ACL:
        - list of groups who can change what's in this set / delete it
        - list of groups who can submit to this problem
